HEADWORD: Subpetiolar
<hw>Sub*pet"i*o*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Concealed within the base of the petiole, as the leaf buds of the
plane tree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

